# 🌿 ECHO Herbal Garden Website

## 📌 Project Title
**ECHO Herbal Garden Website** – *Empowering Communities through Herbal Outreach (ECHO)*

## 🧠 Project Abstract
A virtual herbal garden promoting **AYUSH** (Ayurveda, Yoga, Unani, Siddha, Homeopathy) by preserving and disseminating knowledge on medicinal plants. This platform offers users educational content, interactive exploration, and sustainable healthcare insights.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Educate users about Indian medicinal plants and their benefits
- Promote Indian AYUSH systems
- Create an interactive virtual garden experience
- Aid students, researchers, and healthcare practitioners
- Encourage sustainable health practices

---

## 🔍 Key Features
✅ Browse/search medicinal plants  
✅ Search by disease, symptom, or herb name  
✅ Detailed plant info: names, uses, images, preparation  
✅ Downloadable herbal guides (PDF)  
✅ Mobile responsive design  
✅ Optional: Virtual Garden map & Admin Panel  

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack
| Layer | Technologies |
|-------|--------------|
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Bootstrap/Tailwind CSS |
| Backend | Python (Flask/Django) or Node.js (Express) |
| Database | MongoDB / MySQL / SQLite |
| Tools | GitHub, Figma, Canva, Netlify/Heroku, Postman |

---

## 🧩 Modules / Components
- 🏠 Home Page  
- 🔍 Explore Plants  
- 🌿 Plant Detail View  
- 🔎 Search & Filter  
- 🛒 Purchase Products (Optional)  
- 🧘‍♂️ About AYUSH  
- 📩 Contact / Feedback  
- 🔐 Admin Panel *(Optional)*  

